{"tid":1604004,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚發咗個夢，夢見廿萬香港人衝咗去新屋嶺","createTime":"2019-09-29T23:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T07:34:29.000Z","uid":18835,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3fa82fba9e1e377c04cb767a8c10f280348e9a19","tid":1604004,"uid":18835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T23:55:22.000Z","msg":"放火既放火，救人既救人，殺狗既殺狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後一個個義士俾我地抱返出黎，<br />\n<br />\n可惜佢地已經精神崩潰，滿身是血<br />\n<br />\n我地同義士講：唔洗驚，<br />\n我地黎接你返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家臉上都流住開心既眼淚，<br />\n<br />\n最後大家一齊歡呼，回家。<br />\n<br />\n起身果時流咗幾滴眼淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為我知道以上既情節現實唔會發生。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da261526ed3d8ba415e57e0b6033263033fb43c","tid":1604004,"uid":77220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T23:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b055fbb637e95c4c55f2c4ddb5b8b1c57ad8b8","tid":1604004,"uid":193233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:00:22.000Z","msg":"好可惜冇可能起香港發生！"},{"pid":"004168b1c88bc790ef390e17d52898d64ccd316b","tid":1604004,"uid":166506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:27:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88eabcbaebdb3df4aeafda72f8be332be2e88830","tid":1604004,"uid":47020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:29:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2503a9ed5655c2c3e64ba3c126ea9f7b67305a1f","tid":1604004,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile